affecting PSCs by", "bbox": [665.0, 466.9, 1142.6, 487.8]}, {"text": "18,000 BOE per day.  Daily sales volumes were 731,000", "bbox": [665.0, 488.5, 1142.6, 509.5]}, {"text": "BOE in the twelve months of 2011, compared with", "bbox": [665.0, 510.0, 1142.8, 531.0]}, {"text": "705,000 BOE for 2010.", "bbox": [665.0, 531.7, 862.0, 552.6]}, {"text": "Oil and gas segment earnings in 2010 were", "bbox": [693.1, 553.2, 1142.5, 574.1]}, {"text": "$7.2 billion compared to $5.1 billion in 2009.  The", "bbox": [665.0, 574.8, 1142.6, 595.7]}, {"text": "increase reflected higher average worldwide oil, NGL", "bbox": [665.0, 596.3, 1142.5, 617.2]}, {"text": "and domestic natural gas prices and higher volumes,", "bbox": [665.0, 617.9, 1142.6, 638.8]}, {"text": "partially offset by higher operating expenses partly", "bbox": [665.0, 639.4, 1142.7, 660.3]}, {"text": "resulting from fully expensing CO2, higher field support", "bbox": [665.0, 661.0, 1142.8, 682.8]}, {"text": "and workover expenses and higher DD&A rates.", "bbox": [665.0, 682.5, 1082.2, 703.5]}, {"text": "Daily oil and gas production volumes were 711,000", "bbox": [693.1, 704.2, 1142.6, 725.1]}, {"text": "BOE for 2010, compared with 677,000 BOE for 2009.", "bbox": [665.0, 725.7, 1147.9, 746.6]}, {"text": "The increase was mainly due to the new production in", "bbox": [665.0, 747.3, 1142.5, 768.2]}, {"text": "Bahrain, higher production in the Mukhaizna Field in", "bbox": [665.0, 768.8, 1142.6, 789.7]}, {"text": "Oman, and gas production from domestic assets, which", "bbox": [665.0, 790.4, 1142.7, 811.3]}, {"text": "were partially offset by a decline in Colombia.", "bbox": [665.0, 811.9, 1147.8, 832.8]}, {"text": "Production was negatively impacted in the Middle", "bbox": [665.0, 833.5, 1142.7, 854.5]}, {"text": "East/North Africa, Long Beach and Colombia by higher", "bbox": [665.0, 855.0, 1142.6, 876.0]}, {"text": "year-over-year average oil prices affecting PSCs by", "bbox": [665.0, 876.5, 1142.6, 897.5]}, {"text": "16,000 BOE per day.  Daily sales volumes were 705,000", "bbox": [665.0, 898.2, 1142.6, 919.1]}, {"text": "BOE in the twelve months of 2010, compared with", "bbox": [665.0, 919.7, 1142.8, 940.6]}, {"text": "678,000 BOE for 2009.", "bbox": [665.0, 941.3, 861.9, 962.2]}, {"text": "Oil and gas segment earnings in 2011 include pre-tax", "bbox": [693.1, 962.8, 1142.9, 983.7]}, {"text": "charges of $35 million related to exploration write-offs in", "bbox": [665.0, 984.4, 1142.5, 1005.3]}, {"text": "Libya and $29 million related to Colombia net worth tax,", "bbox": [665.0, 1005.9, 1142.7, 1026.8]}, {"text": "as well as a pre-tax gain for sale of an interest in a", "bbox": [665.0, 1027.5, 1142.6, 1048.5]}, {"text": "Colombian pipeline of $22 million.", "bbox": [665.0, 1049.0, 961.1, 1070.0]}, {"text": "Oil and gas segment earnings in 2010 included a", "bbox": [693.1, 1070.7, 1142.7, 1091.6]}, {"text": "pre-tax charge of $275 million for asset impairments,", "bbox": [665.0, 1092.2, 1142.7, 1113.1]}, {"text": "predominately of gas properties in the Rocky Mountain", "bbox": [665.0, 1113.8, 1142.6, 1134.7]}, {"text": "region.  Oil and gas segment earnings in 2009 included", "bbox": [665.0, 1135.3, 1142.7, 1156.2]}, {"text": "an $8 million pre-tax charge for the termination of rig", "bbox": [665.0, 1156.9, 1142.5, 1177.8]}, {"text": "contracts.", "bbox": [665.0, 1178.4, 762.0, 1199.3]}, {"text": "Average production costs for 2011, excluding taxes", "bbox": [693.1, 1200.0, 1142.5, 1221.0]}, {"text": "other than on income, were $12.84 per BOE, compared", "bbox": [665.0, 1221.5, 1142.8, 1242.5]}, {"text": "to $10.19 for 2010.  The increase resulted from higher", "bbox": [665.0, 1243.2, 1142.5, 1264.1]}, {"text": "workover and well maintenance activity driven by", "bbox": [665.0, 1264.7, 1142.6, 1285.6]}, {"text": "Occidental’s program to increase production at current", "bbox": [665.0, 1286.3, 1142.7, 1307.2]}, {"text": "increased oil prices.  We expect further increases in the", "bbox"